dct_title_s: New Mexico / prepared for Chevron Oil Company, Western Division ; H.M. Gousha Company.
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by spot heights. "© the H.M. Gousha Company" Includes index. Indexs of: public recreation areas, New Mexico mileage chart. and 8 ancillary maps (Roswell New Mexico, El Paso Texas, Albuquerque and vicinity, inset of central Albuquerque, inset of central Santa Fe, Santa Fe and vicinity, Carlsbad Caverns National Park, inset of Carlsbad Caverns National Park and vicinity) on verso. Maps on verso:Roswell New Mexico --  El Paso Texas -- Albuquerque and vicinity-- Central Albuquerque -- Central Santa Fe --  Santa Fe and vicinity -- Carlsbad Caverns National Park -- Carlsbad Caverns National Park.
